      <h2>What We Audit (19 Checks, 4 Categories)</h2>

      <div class="gbp-check-grid">
        <div class="gbp-check-item">
          <span class="gbp-check-icon">&#10003;</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Can Customers Find You?</strong>
            <p>Google title, description, city targeting, schema data, sitemap, headline, content depth</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="gbp-check-item">
          <span class="gbp-check-icon">&#10003;</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Can Customers Reach You?</strong>
            <p>Contact form, tap-to-call, after-hours AI capture, Google Maps embed</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="gbp-check-item">
          <span class="gbp-check-icon">&#10003;</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Does Your Site Build Trust?</strong>
            <p>Reviews, social proof, social media links, sharing previews, image SEO</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="gbp-check-item">
          <span class="gbp-check-icon">&#10003;</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Speed &amp; Security</strong>
            <p>HTTPS, page load time, mobile responsiveness</p>
          </div>
        </div>
