      <div class="gbp-callout">
        <p>"Most businesses we audit score between 30-60 out of 100. The gaps we find typically represent $2,000-$8,000 per month in revenue that's going to competitors instead. We show you exactly where those dollars are going."</p>
        <div class="quote-author">— Kevin Freeland, Founder</div>
      </div>

      <h2>How It Works</h2>

      <ol class="gbp-steps">
        <li><div><strong>Enter your business info</strong> — takes 30 seconds. We need your website URL and city to run the scan.</div></li>
        <li><div><strong>Our system scans 19 data points</strong> — we check everything from your Google search appearance to page speed and trust signals.</div></li>
        <li><div><strong>You get a branded report</strong> — emailed to you with your score, what's broken, and a dollar amount for each issue.</div></li>
        <li><div><strong>Optional: 15-minute strategy call</strong> — walk through the findings together. Zero pressure, zero obligation.</div></li>
      </ol>

      <div class="post-callout">
        <p><strong>Why This Matters</strong></p>
        <p>46% of all Google searches have local intent. If your website, Google profile, and marketing aren't working together, you're invisible to nearly half the people searching for what you sell. The businesses that show up in Google's top results get 44% of the clicks. Everyone else fights over the scraps.</p>
      </div>

      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Is this really free?</summary>
          <p>Yes — 100% free. No credit card, no hidden fees. We provide the audit because it helps business owners see what they're missing. If you want help fixing what we find, we're here. If not, the report is yours to keep.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What exactly do you check?</summary>
          <p>19 data points across 4 categories: findability (can Google show you to local customers?), reachability (can visitors contact you easily?), trust signals (do you look credible?), and technical performance (is your site fast and secure?). Each check is scored and comes with a specific fix.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How fast do I get the report?</summary>
          <p>The automated scan runs within minutes of submitting your info. Kevin personally reviews every report before it goes out — most are delivered within 2 hours, always within 24 hours.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Do I need a Google Business Profile?</summary>
          <p>No — we audit your website and overall online presence regardless. If you don't have a Google Business Profile set up yet, that's actually one of the biggest findings we'll flag, because it means you're missing out on the entire local search channel.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Will you try to sell me something?</summary>
          <p>The audit stands on its own. We'll show you what's broken and how to fix it — many of the fixes are things you can do yourself for free. If you want us to handle the implementation, we can discuss that, but there's zero pressure.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What makes this different from other free audits?</summary>
          <p>Most free audits are generic templates. Ours runs a real scan of your actual website and gives you a score out of 100 with specific dollar estimates for every gap. Plus Kevin personally reviews every report before it goes out.</p>
        </details>
      </div>

      <div class="post-cta-box">
        <h3>Stop Guessing. Start Growing.</h3>
        <p>Find out your score and exactly what to fix — completely free.</p>
        <a href="#gbp-audit-form" class="btn-primary btn-large">Get My Free Business Audit &rarr;</a>
      </div>

    </div>

  </article>

  <script>
    (function() {
      var form = document.getElementById('gbp-audit-form');
      var submitBtn = document.getElementById('gbp-submit-btn');
      var errorBox = document.getElementById('gbp-audit-error');
      if (!form) return;

      function showError(msg) {
        if (!errorBox) return;
        errorBox.textContent = msg;
        errorBox.style.display = 'block';
      }

      form.addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
        // Take over submission so we can wait for the audit + email-queue
        // confirmation before sending the user to the thank-you page.
        e.preventDefault();

        var data = {
          business_name: form.querySelector('[name="business_name"]').value,
          email: form.querySelector('[name="email"]').value,
          website: form.querySelector('[name="website"]').value,
          city: form.querySelector('[name="city"]').value,
          industry: form.querySelector('[name="industry"]').value,
          phone: form.querySelector('[name="phone"]').value,
          source: 'business-audit-landing-page',
          timestamp: new Date().toISOString()
        };

        if (errorBox) errorBox.style.display = 'none';
        submitBtn.textContent = 'Running your audit... (up to 30s)';
        submitBtn.disabled = true;

        // Lead-capture backup: Web3Forms via JSON POST (no navigation).
        // Always sends regardless of audit outcome so the lead isn't lost.
        var web3formsPayload = Object.assign({}, data, {
          access_key: 'af9a5ef5-c8be-450b-8fdd-9039551baa76',
          subject: 'Free Business Audit Request — Lead Magnet'
        });
        fetch('https://api.web3forms.com/submit', {
          method: 'POST',
          headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json', Accept: 'application/json' },
          body: JSON.stringify(web3formsPayload)
        }).catch(function() { /* backup channel — non-blocking */ });

        // Also ping the n8n drip-sequence webhook. sendBeacon is reliable
        // even if the page closes mid-flight.
        try {
          navigator.sendBeacon(
            'https://freelandme.app.n8n.cloud/webhook/business-audit',
            new Blob([JSON.stringify(data)], { type: 'application/json' })
          );
        } catch (err) { /* best-effort */ }

        // Primary path: Netlify Function runs the audit and queues the
        // branded report email through n8n. Only redirect to thank-you
        // once we have confirmation the email is queued.
        fetch('/.netlify/functions/business-audit', {
          method: 'POST',
          headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
          body: JSON.stringify(data)
        }).then(function(resp) {
          return resp.json().then(function(body) {
            if (resp.ok && body && body.emailQueued) {
              window.location.href = '/free-business-audit/thank-you/';
            } else {
              submitBtn.textContent = 'Get My Free Business Audit →';
              submitBtn.disabled = false;
              showError("We received your request but the audit pipeline hit a snag. Kevin was notified and will email your report manually within the hour. No action needed on your end.");
            }
          });
        }).catch(function() {
          submitBtn.textContent = 'Get My Free Business Audit →';
          submitBtn.disabled = false;
          showError("Connection issue running the audit. Your info was received — Kevin will email your report manually within the hour.");
        });
      });
    })();
  </script>

{% endblock %}
